        a: `<h4>ASIA Examination 標準流程</h4>

<p><strong>正式名稱：International Standards for Neurological Classification of Spinal Cord Injury (ISNCSCI)</strong>，由 ASIA + ISCoS 維護，每幾年更新一次（最新 2019 版）。</p>

<h4>1. Sensory Examination</h4>

<p><strong>28 個 key dermatomes 兩側</strong>（C2 到 S4/5）：</p>
<ul>
<li>每個 dermatome 測 <strong>pinprick</strong> + <strong>light touch</strong></li>
<li>計分：0 = absent、1 = altered、2 = normal、NT = not testable</li>
<li>每側總分上限 56（28 × 2）；兩種感覺各 112 分</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>關鍵 dermatome landmarks：</strong></p>
<table>
<tr><th>Level</th><th>Landmark</th></tr>
<tr><td>C2</td><td>後枕</td></tr>
<tr><td>C4</td><td>鎖骨上窩</td></tr>
<tr><td>C7</td><td>中指</td></tr>
<tr><td>T4</td><td>乳頭</td></tr>
<tr><td>T6</td><td>劍突</td></tr>
<tr><td>T10</td><td>肚臍</td></tr>
<tr><td>L1</td><td>腹股溝</td></tr>
<tr><td>L4</td><td>內踝</td></tr>
<tr><td>L5</td><td>第 3 蹠骨背</td></tr>
<tr><td>S1</td><td>外踝</td></tr>
<tr><td>S2-S4/5</td><td>會陰</td></tr>
</table>

<h4>2. Motor Examination</h4>

<p><strong>10 個 key muscles 兩側：</strong></p>
<table>
<tr><th>Level</th><th>Muscle</th><th>動作</th></tr>
<tr><td>C5</td><td>Biceps</td><td>Elbow flexion</td></tr>
<tr><td>C6</td><td>ECRL/ECRB</td><td>Wrist extension</td></tr>
<tr><td>C7</td><td>Triceps</td><td>Elbow extension</td></tr>
<tr><td>C8</td><td>FDP（中指）</td><td>Finger flexion</td></tr>
<tr><td>T1</td><td>ADM</td><td>Finger abduction</td></tr>
<tr><td>L2</td><td>Iliopsoas</td><td>Hip flexion</td></tr>
<tr><td>L3</td><td>Quadriceps</td><td>Knee extension</td></tr>
<tr><td>L4</td><td>Tibialis anterior</td><td>Ankle dorsiflexion</td></tr>
<tr><td>L5</td><td>EHL</td><td>Great toe extension</td></tr>
<tr><td>S1</td><td>Gastrocnemius</td><td>Ankle plantarflexion</td></tr>
</table>

<p><strong>計分</strong>：0-5 MMT；每側上限 50（5 上肢 + 5 下肢 × 5）；兩側總分 100。</p>

<h4>3. Sacral Examination（決定 complete vs incomplete 關鍵）</h4>

<ul>
<li><strong>S4/5 light touch + pinprick</strong>：肛門周圍</li>
<li><strong>Deep Anal Pressure (DAP)</strong>：肛診壓 anorectal junction，病人是否能感覺到 pressure（yes/no）</li>
<li><strong>Voluntary Anal Contraction (VAC)</strong>：請病人收縮肛門，肛診感覺收縮（yes/no）</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Sacral sparing 定義</strong>：S4-5 light touch 或 pinprick 任一存在、或 DAP +、或 VAC + → 即有 sacral sparing → incomplete injury</p>

<h4>4. 決定 Levels</h4>

<p><strong>Sensory Level</strong>：兩側分別最 caudal 的 normal（pinprick + light touch 都 = 2）的 dermatome</p>

<p><strong>Motor Level</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li>有 myotome 的 levels：那個 key muscle 力量 ≥ 3 且其上所有 muscles = 5</li>
<li>沒有 myotome 的 levels（T2-L1, S2-S5）：等於 sensory level</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Neurological Level of Injury (NLI)</strong>：sensory + motor levels 中 most rostral</p>

<p><strong>Zone of Partial Preservation (ZPP)</strong>：在 complete injury（AIS A）下，NLI 以下仍有 partial 功能的 dermatomes/myotomes 範圍</p>

<h4>5. AIS Grade</h4>

<table>
<tr><th>Grade</th><th>定義</th></tr>
<tr><td><strong>A</strong></td><td>Complete：no sensory or motor below NLI，NO sacral sparing（無 S4-5 sensation、無 VAC）</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>B</strong></td><td>Sensory incomplete：有 sacral sensory sparing，但無 motor function more than 3 levels below motor level（兩側）</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>C</strong></td><td>Motor incomplete：有 motor function below NLI（including VAC 或 motor &gt; 3 levels below motor level），但 &lt; 50% key muscles below NLI ≥ 3</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>D</strong></td><td>Motor incomplete：≥ 50% key muscles below NLI ≥ 3</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>E</strong></td><td>Normal：previously 有 deficit 但已恢復</td></tr>
</table>

