<h4>機轉</h4>

<p><strong>多因素：</strong></p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Blood breakdown products</strong>：oxyhemoglobin → free radicals → endothelial damage</li>
<li><strong>Vasoactive 物質失衡</strong>：endothelin-1 ↑、NO 與 prostacyclin ↓</li>
<li><strong>Smooth muscle hypercontraction</strong>：calcium influx</li>
<li><strong>Inflammation</strong>：cytokines、complement、leukocyte adhesion</li>
<li><strong>Apoptosis</strong>：endothelial cell death</li>
<li><strong>Cortical Spreading Depolarization</strong>：近年研究指出對 DCI 也有貢獻</li>
<li><strong>Microthrombosis</strong>：除了 large vessel spasm，micro-circulation 也受損</li>
</ol>

<p><strong>結果：</strong>cerebral perfusion ↓ → ischemia → 若 prolong → infarction（DCI）→ neurological deficit</p>

<h4>DCI（Delayed Cerebral Ischemia）</h4>

<p><strong>定義（Vergouwen 2010 consensus）：</strong></p>
<ul>
